Package: SVMCwebr
Title: Full SVMC Model for WebR
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("HAMK", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "olli.niemitalo@hamk.fi"),
    person("Hui", "Tang", role = "aut",
           comment = "Original SVMC Fortran code (huitang-earth/SVMC)")
    )
Description: WebR-compatible R wrapper for the full SVMC (Simple Vegetation
    Model of Carbon). Provides the complete integration loop: P-hydro
    photosynthesis-hydraulics optimization (with L-BFGS-B), SpaFHy canopy and
    soil water balance, YASSO20 soil carbon decomposition, and carbon allocation.
    All file I/O (NetCDF, namelists) is replaced by R-level data passing.
    The Fortran source derives from vendor/SVMC with minimal modifications for
    R compatibility (see src/ headers for provenance).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
